*Dečak* je igrao fudbal. (The boy was playing football.)
On je došao sa svojim *dečakom*. (He came with his boy.)
Ona je imala jednog *dečaka*. (She had one boy.)
*Dečak* je bio veoma uspešan u školi. (The boy was very successful in school.)
Ona voli da se igrate sa svojim *dečakom*. (She likes to play with her boy.)
Učitelji su bili oduševljeni sa *dečakom*. (The teachers were delighted with the boy.)